data.meta_description: Lippincott, 1959. 1st Ed. 5th Ptg. 8Vo Hardcover. Good / Poor. Item #93106 254pp. Black boards, tricolor lettering and graphics on spine and front board, unclipped jacket. Text is clean on unmarked, uncreased pages. Hinges are secure, textblock is square with pointed corners, shallow foredge water wrinkle on some center signatures. Moderate+ overall book shelf/timewear, foxing on inner
